{"tid":2299100,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人捉過買走私煙嘅入黎！","createTime":"2020-11-24T13:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T15:16:40.000Z","uid":146861,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8006e40fb29e4e94e619c6f4c93e4a7781f08ea9","tid":2299100,"uid":146861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"俾人捉到買私煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人有經驗分享下<br />\n會唔會留案底<br />\n<br />\n利申：幫朋友問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef71d07869729d5c10ce097c096cc1941373315e","tid":2299100,"uid":116891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8006e40fb29e4e94e619c6f4c93e4a7781f08ea9","tid":2299100,"uid":146861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"俾人捉到買私煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人有經驗分享下<br />\n會唔會留案底<br />\n<br />\n利申：幫朋友問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"Buy or sell？<br />\n識人做拆家<br />\n被海關起左個倉當場斷到正<br />\n上到庭個官判左十幾個月監<br />\n兼且逐枝煙仔計罰款"},{"pid":"d12b7f6fdb5b78afc745d223f94eac3a3615fedb","tid":2299100,"uid":3744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611c260d86add5337aa678ca49384ae8acc72620","tid":2299100,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"會留案底"},{"pid":"8cd5e5220ec1ac6daac941cc2523fc8a370ca101","tid":2299100,"uid":195046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:45:56.000Z","msg":"本港目前有多條法例，訂明走私香煙屬刑事罪行。<br />\n根據《進出口條例》(第60章)，可公訴走私罪行的<br />\n最高刑罰為監禁七年和罰款二百萬元。不按照<br />\n《應課稅品條例》(第109章)所訂條文而入口、管有<br />\n或購買應課稅品，也屬刑事罪行。《應課稅品條例》<br />\n曾在一九九五年修訂，最高刑罰由罰款十萬元增至一<br />\n百萬元，最長刑期為監禁兩年，藉以阻嚇走私、非法<br />\n分銷和零售應課稅品活動。自一九九五年生效的《有<br />\n組織及嚴重罪行條例》(第455章)，使當局可進一步加<br />\n重走私煙販的刑罰和充公其走私得益<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afa2e1a6c3a3e594ea5ee6b2cf8892125c84891","tid":2299100,"uid":195046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"香港海關關長袁銘輝於2011年1月31在&ldquo;2010年工作回顧記者會&rdquo;上發表的總結的文中提到：&ldquo;我們會繼續加強宣傳，呼籲市民和業界舉報私煙活動，與及提醒市民購買私煙其實與販賣私煙一樣均屬違法，罪成亦會留有案底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7917350fa31619d3b541008433ca8463e66ad53","tid":2299100,"uid":187987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"識人走貨通常都要坐<br />\n88啦監躉"},{"pid":"69c6e8b41bd55f0036e126c2b5e4b43c38375152","tid":2299100,"uid":236780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"衰咩入黎呀?<br />\n買煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311cfaa90971eaabbf85459b543dab71eb654da3","tid":2299100,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:48:52.000Z","msg":"買點判"},{"pid":"b76ed1548e397d83b71d24898e781ee1b58038a9","tid":2299100,"uid":244105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"買家斷正?<br />\n唔係點捉"},{"pid":"650bb9caf159271e41c7af38c58cac77003ee6ee","tid":2299100,"uid":146861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"個朋友係買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />